2024/12/16 12:57:04 Commit: {"did":"did:plc:gjsoejzm7at4syhrvzgizrev","time_us":1734353824040293,"kind":"commit","commit":{"rev":"3ldgevski2i2v","operation":"create","collection":"app.bsky.feed.post","rkey":"3ldgevkceec2x","record":{"$type":"app.bsky.feed.post","createdAt":"2024-12-16T12:56:54.287Z","embed":{"$type":"app.bsky.embed.images","images":[{"alt":"Rear of an Indian private bus with an image of a child wearing a Santa hat.","aspectRatio":{"height":1087,"width":1080},"image":{"$type":"blob","ref":{"$link":"bafkreig2tc7ew2yh3lqgtivv4hc4agi7wfjuaivwwughvww673auzlyqea"},"mimeType":"image/jpeg","size":742759}}]},"facets":[{"features":[{"$type":"app.bsky.richtext.facet#tag","tag":"Photography"}],"index":{"byteEnd":279,"byteStart":267}},{"features":[{"$type":"app.bsky.richtext.facet#tag","tag":"SpéirGorm"}],"index":{"byteEnd":291,"byteStart":280}},{"features":[{"$type":"app.bsky.richtext.facet#tag","tag":"IndiaSky"}],"index":{"byteEnd":301,"byteStart":292}}],"langs":["en"],"text":"'There's Something About Merry'\n\nChristmas in India is always a little surreal.\n\nOutside of the tiny Christian population, there's little to tell it is actually happening - no carols, no ornament-laden trees, no manic advertising. \n\nBut when you least expect it ...\n\n#Photography #SpéirGorm #IndiaSky"},"cid":"bafyreibevxcnd5f6456v3bpbhk53j6ezvr3qfh2dconmyzmk42mdbamr34"}}
2024/12/16 12:57:04 Commit: {"did":"did:plc:jqequyk45blaix5zz3xvxvou","time_us":1734353824044065,"kind":"commit","commit":{"rev":"3ldgevthi2i25","operation":"create","collection":"app.bsky.feed.post","rkey":"3ldgevt556s2o","record":{"$type":"app.bsky.feed.post","createdAt":"2024-12-16T12:57:03.567Z","langs":["en"],"reply":{"parent":{"cid":"bafyreiatjp3mk75hapvts6t6md654q4byto5nn5toxk7ybwwc56pmmut4e","uri":"at://did:plc:4aaq2yk2liwonz6adtfoz2pr/app.bsky.feed.post/3ldg73cb5b22e"},"root":{"cid":"bafyreiatjp3mk75hapvts6t6md654q4byto5nn5toxk7ybwwc56pmmut4e","uri":"at://did:plc:4aaq2yk2liwonz6adtfoz2pr/app.bsky.feed.post/3ldg73cb5b22e"}},"text":"First of all: I love her.\n\nAs far as book recommendations, all information on her is very scarce. The other comment recommending Road to Hel, I agree that’s as close as it gets but it’s all archeological finds that show what Viking funeral rites were like and how they changed through the ages. (1/2)"},"cid":"bafyreicymff65yu7p3gpzp5eshb3rhxozy6epnqmirfeyg2bngcqym57ji"}}
