2024/12/16 12:57:13 Commit: {"did":"did:plc:2cbckttc7gpexwhpmifmetab","time_us":1734353832999287,"kind":"commit","commit":{"rev":"3ldgew2wj4s2q","operation":"create","collection":"app.bsky.feed.post","rkey":"3ldgevqlzic2r","record":{"$type":"app.bsky.feed.post","createdAt":"2024-12-16T12:57:00.903Z","embed":{"$type":"app.bsky.embed.images","images":[{"alt":"","aspectRatio":{"height":1999,"width":1885},"image":{"$type":"blob","ref":{"$link":"bafkreih3sznsdys7n3wlfsd2dfjlw6uwmjpjs4lku4mmg7tmcgfgtq2dty"},"mimeType":"image/jpeg","size":895927}},{"alt":"","aspectRatio":{"height":1999,"width":1483},"image":{"$type":"blob","ref":{"$link":"bafkreibinxezzpr6pbwp2s4yoeebbdrwcgpjk5odetedv2z32cgamzh54q"},"mimeType":"image/jpeg","size":778916}},{"alt":"","aspectRatio":{"height":2000,"width":1713},"image":{"$type":"blob","ref":{"$link":"bafkreiaaw274cescg7kwnjvlxbn3fh7tywwzklmmao5uemwfc2g6i5gfei"},"mimeType":"image/jpeg","size":828106}},{"alt":"","aspectRatio":{"height":2000,"width":1225},"image":{"$type":"blob","ref":{"$link":"bafkreiehhz2r56posjc7oftztfak6h5uzvpxmqu46mxzib3qs7vy7ebuua"},"mimeType":"image/jpeg","size":613656}}]},"langs":["zh"],"text":"【CWT68來場感謝】\n非常感謝前來認親與被我認親的各位！！！感謝你們用這麼多美麗的卡片與讓我可以好幾天不吃飯的零食量來砸我！！😭🫶\n我好喜歡！！！我很抱歉給零食的各位！！不是被我吃掉就是被我藏起來過冬（？）所以沒拍！！！但我真的好喜歡！！！！超級謝謝！！！！\n\n我很抱歉這場又是（又）因為學業而導致一直當機的焰炎👉👈\n語言組織不能\u0026可能說出傷到人的話這兩點我在現在睡飽的狀態下感到很懊悔😭\n真的很對不起！！！！也很謝謝不嫌棄這樣的我的你們好愛你們我哭死！！！\n（文還有一點，下繼續）"},"cid":"bafyreiaiowxiur6mtwcvlyhvrv2twobvyq6rdhkpagczgq2ly7jhhh6jfu"}}
2024/12/16 12:57:13 Commit: {"did":"did:plc:shaw32n65hmx5chfpmhujsro","time_us":1734353833006288,"kind":"commit","commit":{"rev":"3ldgew3wifp22","operation":"create","collection":"app.bsky.feed.post","rkey":"3ldgew3wttk2d","record":{"$type":"app.bsky.feed.post","createdAt":"2024-12-16T12:57:12.798Z","langs":["en"],"text":"I finally gathered up the money to grab Grounded, I've been looking to get that game for a while now, because why not face the arachnophobia I don't have by decimating the local orb weaver population\n\nPeople should get shrunk more. There I said it, is there a PROBLEM get shrunk idiot get shrunk get-"},"cid":"bafyreihclxr6g4qk6ojspgdfdoudvwaafh2inwvc5iyzn2kzau3j3g6s5u"}}
2024/12/16 12:57:13 Commit: {"did":"did:plc:325mzxrpo7kfegumi4ubuzrb","time_us":1734353833028480,"kind":"commit","commit":{"rev":"3ldgew3wamu2q","operation":"create","collection":"app.bsky.feed.post","rkey":"3ldgew3hmjs27","record":{"$type":"app.bsky.feed.post","createdAt":"2024-12-16T12:57:12.296Z","embed":{"$type":"app.bsky.embed.record","record":{"cid":"bafyreidouj7y4tqfcgffjnpf7epspcbbslsuhzendvurmudf6wac5tqsbm","uri":"at://did:plc:sv2ivxvf7fxchmo2xamo3wwx/app.bsky.feed.post/3lddk36o3ns2k"}},"langs":["es"],"text":"Yo 51k y este ha sido un año bastante musical. \nLa música en mi creo rellena huecos de la cotidianeidad, de la rutina que sino se hacen excesivamente monótonos y solitarios. \nEl artículo habla del silencio, me preguntó si eso existe, rodeados de ruidos constantes"},"cid":"bafyreianvmukzpydzxpxmgoqxdkjynsvvkb3f4z3reaylwqoiu7tbjyl7y"}}
2024/12/16 12:57:13 Commit: {"did":"did:plc:325mzxrpo7kfegumi4ubuzrb","time_us":1734353833029171,"kind":"commit","commit":{"rev":"3ldgew3wamu2q","operation":"create","collection":"app.bsky.feed.post","rkey":"3ldgew3jf6c27","record":{"$type":"app.bsky.feed.post","createdAt":"2024-12-16T12:57:12.297Z","langs":["es"],"reply":{"parent":{"cid":"bafyreianvmukzpydzxpxmgoqxdkjynsvvkb3f4z3reaylwqoiu7tbjyl7y","uri":"at://did:plc:325mzxrpo7kfegumi4ubuzrb/app.bsky.feed.post/3ldgew3hmjs27"},"root":{"cid":"bafyreianvmukzpydzxpxmgoqxdkjynsvvkb3f4z3reaylwqoiu7tbjyl7y","uri":"at://did:plc:325mzxrpo7kfegumi4ubuzrb/app.bsky.feed.post/3ldgew3hmjs27"}},"text":"Algunos al quedarnos nosotros en silencio podemos escuchar la música de los pájaros, los árboles moviéndose x el viento...si los ladridos de perros nos lo permiten. Pero otros cuando quedan en silencio oyen el ruido de unos ventiladores de ordenador o coches y ambulancias"},"cid":"bafyreicdzz7odd4tcjrtgbdwlpszbl4e7pt5yd3i7b3uwgsnymqikyosua"}}
2024/12/16 12:57:13 Commit: {"did":"did:plc:325mzxrpo7kfegumi4ubuzrb","time_us":1734353833029654,"kind":"commit","commit":{"rev":"3ldgew3wamu2q","operation":"create","collection":"app.bsky.feed.post","rkey":"3ldgew3jkzs27","record":{"$type":"app.bsky.feed.post","createdAt":"2024-12-16T12:57:12.298Z","langs":["es"],"reply":{"parent":{"cid":"bafyreicdzz7odd4tcjrtgbdwlpszbl4e7pt5yd3i7b3uwgsnymqikyosua","uri":"at://did:plc:325mzxrpo7kfegumi4ubuzrb/app.bsky.feed.post/3ldgew3jf6c27"},"root":{"cid":"bafyreianvmukzpydzxpxmgoqxdkjynsvvkb3f4z3reaylwqoiu7tbjyl7y","uri":"at://did:plc:325mzxrpo7kfegumi4ubuzrb/app.bsky.feed.post/3ldgew3hmjs27"}},"text":"No estoy muy convencida de que se piense mejor con ruidos que con musica, porque incluso, aunque está tenga letra, una vez que es conocida, se encuentra en segundo plano y quizá se convierte un poco en ruido, pero un ruido que elegimos, no impuesto por el entorno. El silencioso absoluto es algo..."},"cid":"bafyreicvf6k3rttbv7jg4kjymbfu2i7ayo6oqowtv7p3ig3moezh2cymxe"}}
2024/12/16 12:57:13 Commit: {"did":"did:plc:325mzxrpo7kfegumi4ubuzrb","time_us":1734353833030524,"kind":"commit","commit":{"rev":"3ldgew3wamu2q","operation":"create","collection":"app.bsky.feed.post","rkey":"3ldgew3jqvc27","record":{"$type":"app.bsky.feed.post","createdAt":"2024-12-16T12:57:12.299Z","langs":["es"],"reply":{"parent":{"cid":"bafyreicvf6k3rttbv7jg4kjymbfu2i7ayo6oqowtv7p3ig3moezh2cymxe","uri":"at://did:plc:325mzxrpo7kfegumi4ubuzrb/app.bsky.feed.post/3ldgew3jkzs27"},"root":{"cid":"bafyreianvmukzpydzxpxmgoqxdkjynsvvkb3f4z3reaylwqoiu7tbjyl7y","uri":"at://did:plc:325mzxrpo7kfegumi4ubuzrb/app.bsky.feed.post/3ldgew3hmjs27"}},"text":"Totalmente artificial, que debe uno empeñarse en buscar (bueno capaz que en algunas zonas del planeta, sin vida y sin viento, y sin lluvia...) \nEl silencio, una quimera. \n\nDisfruten de la música, disfruten del ruido y sino lo disfrutan y se lo pueden permitir conviertan el fondo sonoro en música 🫶"},"cid":"bafyreiehdckctvyebnjvkjml7w72em5pooz2xww6ks6bn6x3wnz5w46htq"}}
2024/12/16 12:57:13 Commit: {"did":"did:plc:xkv3yejd3ot36pcenfi2twfb","time_us":1734353833033031,"kind":"commit","commit":{"rev":"3ldgew3zxqg2s","operation":"create","collection":"app.bsky.feed.post","rkey":"3ldgevzgtc22f","record":{"$type":"app.bsky.feed.post","createdAt":"2024-12-16T12:57:10.174Z","langs":["en"],"reply":{"parent":{"cid":"bafyreiceyy37ykwsswombhi46574bnfy7bytvyfkdghbu6xgz2l66uxquy","uri":"at://did:plc:cid355erfljc3myhwjqhej4d/app.bsky.feed.post/3ldfwjshw7c2c"},"root":{"cid":"bafyreiceyy37ykwsswombhi46574bnfy7bytvyfkdghbu6xgz2l66uxquy","uri":"at://did:plc:cid355erfljc3myhwjqhej4d/app.bsky.feed.post/3ldfwjshw7c2c"}},"text":"La verdad si es extraña la cara tan perfectamente de frente, eso lo hacer verse falso. Los cocodrilos y caimanes son animales realmente fascinantes, han cambiado muy poco a lo largo de los años."},"cid":"bafyreihfc2ufoele7hnkuelo4pfcxfmxk27gv6kr3gkxkwyuvx2pjktn5e"}}
2024/12/16 12:57:13 Commit: {"did":"did:plc:ufv53erqkurczzsmi5xhryfe","time_us":1734353833034047,"kind":"commit","commit":{"rev":"3ldgew3yq4z2z","operation":"create","collection":"app.bsky.feed.post","rkey":"3ldgevyw72s2k","record":{"$type":"app.bsky.feed.post","createdAt":"2024-12-16T12:57:09.632Z","langs":["en"],"reply":{"parent":{"cid":"bafyreid2cp4vgtx4x77e7jn3h2yziz6y6qyktebcu3oomymq23uhes3rmq","uri":"at://did:plc:chtgzdtsq3ffyubdkkpry4yd/app.bsky.feed.post/3ldgelsdo322h"},"root":{"cid":"bafyreift4chjphnb6epmpqphrpc7jsz4oymdip6k6orukzhw4xss33qgea","uri":"at://did:plc:ufv53erqkurczzsmi5xhryfe/app.bsky.feed.post/3ldfxrrdyjc2l"}},"text":"Thank you very much! \nI also appreciate your feedback on her hair, which I drew with care!"},"cid":"bafyreif6gmylxfh2sx6m7plsm3anls53vaj4qldgwztb33g3wzmmc5kqsm"}}
