2024/12/16 13:39:11 Commit: {"did":"did:plc:mfuoqj66cu2e5gqagrzejip6","time_us":1734356351248163,"kind":"commit","commit":{"rev":"3ldghb44c232g","operation":"create","collection":"app.bsky.feed.post","rkey":"3ldghazpxuk2v","record":{"$type":"app.bsky.feed.post","createdAt":"2024-12-16T13:39:06.992Z","embed":{"$type":"app.bsky.embed.images","images":[{"alt":"A round little plush owl with big eyes.","aspectRatio":{"height":1493,"width":2000},"image":{"$type":"blob","ref":{"$link":"bafkreicxfwi5ttzwwiv5lsgfxpcry4v2aunqrpgr4bgm26tvfa5earbxnm"},"mimeType":"image/jpeg","size":400394}},{"alt":"The owl with a seltzer can for scale, although I had not yet learned to align them so it gave a more exact idea: the owl is sitting on a box and the seltzer can is in front of it, with an angled view, so it's hard to tell that the owl is much shorter than the can.","aspectRatio":{"height":1493,"width":2000},"image":{"$type":"blob","ref":{"$link":"bafkreic6njubbfhbnxrxurrnsmdrxo2iq2gzlgk6ctvzgnlbjezo6fxw5m"},"mimeType":"image/jpeg","size":414712}}]},"facets":[{"features":[{"$type":"app.bsky.richtext.facet#tag","tag":"artAdventCalendar"}],"index":{"byteEnd":28,"byteStart":10}}],"langs":["en"],"reply":{"parent":{"cid":"bafyreiedvg7xzcnghhpnut3ku66ippyiogouqqmvzwme4vmxac3l5nd2t4","uri":"at://did:plc:mfuoqj66cu2e5gqagrzejip6/app.bsky.feed.post/3ldel3ssy6s2p"},"root":{"cid":"bafyreiep36pforozowjinmyttterdxyjbk27fmsqz3fu4m34cyuwas5jcy","uri":"at://did:plc:mfuoqj66cu2e5gqagrzejip6/app.bsky.feed.post/3lcaxrditi225"}},"text":"Day 16 of #artAdventCalendar : The first in-the-hoop conversion of a plushie. I think I still manually sewed the darts, and it has all kinds of hand-sewn attachments, but here's Choly Knight's owl scaled down to fit a 5x7 embroidery machine, and the first appearance of Aldi Seltzer Can For Scale."},"cid":"bafyreih23lwwvycunygtbxs3yt5wrsunxzghfuwkjrwx7rjpkkf4jtvo34"}}
2024/12/16 13:39:11 Post: {"PostID":"3ldghazpxuk2v","CreatorDid":"did:plc:mfuoqj66cu2e5gqagrzejip6","CreatedAt":"2024-12-16T13:39:06.992Z","Text":"Day 16 of #artAdventCalendar : The first in-the-hoop conversion of a plushie. I think I still manually sewed the darts, and it has all kinds of hand-sewn attachments, but here's Choly Knight's owl scaled down to fit a 5x7 embroidery machine, and the first appearance of Aldi Seltzer Can For Scale.","Tags":["artAdventCalendar"]}
