2024/12/16 13:39:54 Commit: {"did":"did:plc:wduqecvwnwall33jynaq5w5i","time_us":1734356394057673,"kind":"commit","commit":{"rev":"3ldghcge2el2g","operation":"create","collection":"app.bsky.feed.post","rkey":"3ldghcg7ud22c","record":{"$type":"app.bsky.feed.post","createdAt":"2024-12-16T13:39:53.716Z","langs":["ja"],"text":"私がとーきょー⛄️❄️ｾｯｼｮﾝ歌ってる時に\n「部屋でもいいよ！？」\n「クリスマスに部屋は……！」\nって騒いでたの私以外の∕﹨二ﾜ好きにやらない方がいいぞ。ﾌﾙﾎﾞｯｺだから。"},"cid":"bafyreiff7bfbmddmsutxay4sztml4eitukk6d5gldtb5i26qfds6lfn5sa"}}
